{"tid":1723123,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[星期六日行動post]商場和你唱唔等於嘉年華","createTime":"2019-11-15T05:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T03:33:33.000Z","uid":201678,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9ffd4fe9ee04d1a78f6fbaa3d7ead9572bd7b5c4","tid":1723123,"uid":201678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:51:25.000Z","msg":"勇武左一星期係時候要休整一下<br />\n好耐都無聽過願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n黎緊星期六日係時候要係各大商場搞下和理非活動<br />\n一黎可以用呢首極具感染力既歌去團結更多香港人<br />\n二黎一齊回顧番中大誓死守衛家園英勇戰績 拆穿黑警大話<br />\n三黎經濟攬炒 等自由咪再落黎<br />\n<br />\n建議流程<br />\n1. 大合唱願榮光<br />\n2. 文宣組回顧黑警企圖攻入中大 手足誓與中大共存亡 成功擊退黑警<br />\n3. 讀出手足們寫下既遺書 向佢地視死如歸既精神致敬<br />\n4. 分享環節 例如發表理解示威者永不割蓆等宣言<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d19e9866603f5d79bf5e0ce2dfce47667133c60c","tid":1723123,"uid":109389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04a9752d9c414aa6e0837659d4f554fa6a54b74b","tid":1723123,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"[轉守為攻] 將大學要塞化，無限伸展，連結18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"747b5df1ffee374a98866dfa32ed5edbf45d3590","tid":1723123,"uid":201678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78706c9737f1bef4beb26643ff8bff0647f11a24","tid":1723123,"uid":73055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9b883be95ec2d8a5b019a11a88bead302ae2a97","tid":1723123,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"6874cb68e3970103aa21b1ca2febc56f74f19cbf","tid":1723123,"uid":284787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:17:08.000Z"